      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "4. Teein Rahmeem uslez tas\nGaischums Tumtibâ/ tas scheb-\nlignajs / Sirdsschehligajs un\ntaitnajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "5. Labbi tam Zitwekam/ kaê\napschehlojachs/ un labpraht ais-\ndohd/ un apkohtpj kawas Leetas\npareifs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Jo muhscham tas ne tchan-\nbisees/ tas Taifnajs taps muh-\nschtgi peeminnehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Winsch no niknas Slawas\nne bihsees / winna Sirde irr\nstipra/ un pataujahsus to KUN-\nGu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Winna Sirde irr droh-\nfcha/ un ne bibstahs / teekatts\nwinsch pee fatweem Prettineekeem\nPreeku reds.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Winsch iskaisa/ un dohd\nteem Nabbageem/ winna Taif-\nniba paleek muhschigi / winna\nRags taps pa-angstinahts ar\nGohdu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Tas Besdeewigß to re-\ndsehs/ uu apskaitifees / winsch\nfakohdihs fawus Sohbus / un\nnonthks/ to Besdeewigü Kahri-\nba ees bohja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta CXIII. Dseesma.\nIrr weena Pamahzischana us wiſeem Deewa\nKalpeem/kateem buhsDeewu flaweht: 1. Par\ntahm Labdarrijchanahm / ko winsch teem\nNabbageem un Behdigeem parahdijs: 4. etc.\n1. Alleluja: Teizeet juhs\nKalpi ta KUNGA/ tei-\nzeet ta KUNG A\nWahrdu.\n2. Slawehts lai irr ta KUN-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "3. No Saules Uslehfscha-\nlihds winnas No-eefchanai/\nflawehts irr ta KUNGA\nWahrds.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "4. Tas KUNGS irr aug-\npahr wiſeem Pagaxeem/win-\nGohds eet pahr tahm Debbefi\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "5. Kas irr tahds ka\nKUNGS muhsfu Deews?\ntohti angsti irr apfehdees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "6. Kas femmu skattahs De-\nbefis un wins Gemmes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "7. Kas to Nabbagu no Pih-\nleim uszelf / un va-augsti\nto Behdigu no teem Dubteem\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "8. Ka winsch to fehdina p\nLeeleem-Kungeem/ pee fawn La-\nschu Leeleem-Kungeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "9. Kas to Ne-auglign leek\nSaimi dshwoht/ ka ta wee-\npreeziga Behrnu Mahte toh-\nAlleluja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta CXIV. Dseesma.\nIrr weena Vateikschanas Dseesma to Israe-\nBehrnu/par to brihnigu Jswechunu no\ngiptes: 1. Zaur to Juhrn un Jardanu:\nZaur Kalneem un iskaltutcheem Luffn-\nscheem : 4. etc.\n1. Ad Israels no Egypte-\nisgnahje/ Tehkaba Nam-\nno fiveschas Wallo-\nLaudim.\n2. Tad tappe Juhrda winna-\npar fwehtu Dalku / un Israe-\npar winna Walstibu.\n3. Ta Juhra redseja un beh-\ndse / tas Jardans greesehs at-\npaffat.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
